<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" href="assets/xml/rss.xsl" media="all"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>写程序的龙龙</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/</link><description>龙龙的技术博客</description><atom:link href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/rss.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"></atom:link><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Sat, 16 Dec 2017 16:59:34 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>Nikola (getnikola.com)</generator><docs>http://blogs.law.harvard.edu/tech/rss</docs><item><title>CAD练习题26——已知半径之和作图</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-26-yi-zhi-ban-jing-zhi-he-zuo-tu/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;题目：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p26-7.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p26-7.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;这道题还是比较困难的，两个圆的半径不知道，只知道半径的和，画的时候就不好下手，知道弧长120，却不知道圆心的具体位置，只知道一个100，还加上了b的半径。能画的，就剩下了中间一个长度120的直线。这道题是真的有点难度了……&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1、先画原图中唯一已知的一条120直线。由于a和b的半径和是50，并且给定了100的直线，也就是2倍的a+b，外加弧120与b外切，也就意味着，利用半径和50，以及给定的100，构造两个圆，可以确定弧120的圆心。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p26-1.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p26-1.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2、连接交点和两个圆的圆心，可以得到弧120两个端点所在的直线，利用缩放得到120弧。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p26-2.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p26-2.PNG"&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p26-3.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p26-3.PNG"&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p26-4.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p26-4.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3、镜像得到下边的弧120，同时画出两边的圆。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p26-5.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p26-5.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;4、完成并清理图形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p26-6.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p26-6.PNG"&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p26-7.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p26-7.PNG"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>CAD</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-26-yi-zhi-ban-jing-zhi-he-zuo-tu/</guid><pubDate>Sat, 16 Dec 2017 16:34:18 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>CAD练习题25——利用缩放解决成比例边长问题</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-25-li-yong-suo-fang-jie-jue-cheng-bi-li-bian-chang-wen-ti/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;题目：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p25-7.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p25-7.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;这道题的难点在于2倍关系如何实现，在这里我们采用的是缩放。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1、先画已知部分。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p25-1.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p25-1.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2、构造半径2倍关系的两个圆。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p25-2.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p25-2.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3、沿着直角三角形斜边进行缩放。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p25-3.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p25-3.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;4、完成2倍关系。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p25-4.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p25-4.PNG"&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p25-5.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p25-5.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;5、利用起点端点方向画弧，完成其他部分，并清理图形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p25-6.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p25-6.PNG"&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p25-7.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p25-7.PNG"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>CAD</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-25-li-yong-suo-fang-jie-jue-cheng-bi-li-bian-chang-wen-ti/</guid><pubDate>Sat, 16 Dec 2017 16:12:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>CAD练习题24——已知斜边和一条直角边作直角三角形</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-24-yi-zhi-xie-bian-he-yi-tiao-zhi-jiao-bian-zuo-zhi-jiao-san-jiao-xing/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;题目：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p24-6.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p24-6.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;这道题看上去比较乱，最核心的就是如何在已知斜边和一条直角边的情况下，作出直角三角形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1、先画已知的部分。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p24-1.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p24-1.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2、根据已知的斜边和一条直角边，画出直角三角形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p24-2.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p24-2.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3、用同样的原理完成另外两个直角三角形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p24-3.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p24-3.PNG"&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p24-4.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p24-4.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;4、完成其余部分，并清理图形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p24-5.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p24-5.PNG"&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p24-6.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p24-6.PNG"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>CAD</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-24-yi-zhi-xie-bian-he-yi-tiao-zhi-jiao-bian-zuo-zhi-jiao-san-jiao-xing/</guid><pubDate>Sat, 16 Dec 2017 16:00:02 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>CAD练习题23——利用三边相切和缩放解决圆形密铺问题</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-23-li-yong-san-bian-xiang-qie-he-suo-fang-jie-jue-yuan-xing-mi-pu-wen-ti/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;题目：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p23-7.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p23-7.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;这道题需要从外往里画，最后再缩放。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1、构造外部一圈圆形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p23-1.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p23-1.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2、作内切三角形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p23-2.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p23-2.PNG"&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p23-3.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p23-3.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3、作对角线以构造三边相切。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p23-4.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p23-4.PNG"&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p23-5.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p23-5.PNG"&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p23-6.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p23-6.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;4、缩放并清理图形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p23-7.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p23-7.PNG"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>CAD</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-23-li-yong-san-bian-xiang-qie-he-suo-fang-jie-jue-yuan-xing-mi-pu-wen-ti/</guid><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2017 04:19:55 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>CAD练习题22——利用len作指定长度的弧</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/li-yong-lenzuo-zhi-ding-chang-du-de-hu/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;题目：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p22-12.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p22-12.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;这道题只需要注意一个地方，就是指定长度的弧怎么做。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1、先画明显的部分。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p22-1.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p22-1.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2、利用圆作两个对接的弧。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p22-2.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p22-2.PNG"&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p22-3.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p22-3.PNG"&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p22-4.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p22-4.PNG"&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p22-5.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p22-5.PNG"&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p22-6.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p22-6.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3、利用len作指定长度的弧。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p22-7.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p22-7.PNG"&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p22-8.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p22-8.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;4、利用类平行四边形、镜像画弧。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p22-9.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p22-9.PNG"&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p22-10.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p22-10.PNG"&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p22-11.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p22-11.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;5、清理图形&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p22-12.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p22-12.PNG"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>CAD</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/li-yong-lenzuo-zhi-ding-chang-du-de-hu/</guid><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2017 04:01:34 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>设置IE兼容性访问ntce.cn</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/she-zhi-iejian-rong-xing-fang-wen-ntcecn/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;随着IE逐步被淘汰，很多旧网站都会出现兼容性问题。以ntce.cn为例来解决这个问题：&lt;/p&gt;
